Bachelorâ€™s Degree in Packaging, Process Engineering, Chemical Engineering, Mechanical Engineering or related fields;
Minimum of 5-7 years of experience in a manufacturing facility
Minimum of 1-2 years of experience in the food and beverage industry
Consumer packaging experience required
Excellent computer skills including AutoCAD
Strong project management and problem-solving skills
Willingness and ability to work with a culturally rich and diverse workforce
other (travel, special hours or other considerations):
Substantial amount of time spent in manufacturing facility; exposure to allergens and chemicals.
10% travel - to other PacMoore location(s) or customer sites as needed.
PacMoore Products is an Equal Opportunity Employer.
